  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Head behind enemy lines in this <i>vehicle based combat game</i> and destroy everything in your path as you race against the clock to locate and secure stolen nuclear launch codes. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2090100/extras/8da43b73d2b0143ca4937b00ec4b39b7.poster.avif?t=1741195933\" width=320 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2090100/extras/8da43b73d2b0143ca4937b00ec4b39b7.webm?t=1741195933\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2090100/extras/8da43b73d2b0143ca4937b00ec4b39b7.mp4?t=1741195933\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Join the <strong>Extraction Force</strong> today and prepare for battle.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>WISHLIST TO ENLIST!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2090100/extras/a6c4ca7be58dd71e2627897d51e193e5.avif?t=1741195933\" width=600 height=152 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Slow moving but rough and tough. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The perfect tool to bulldoze your way into enemy territory. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2090100/extras/2281fc6356010c4fe8a64771b017b120.avif?t=1741195933\" width=600 height=152 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Equipped with rockets to rain destruction from the sky.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Fast and agile flight allows you to avoid most incoming enemy attacks.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2090100/extras/81115e6f742d97343150329fe24b20c3.avif?t=1741195933\" width=600 height=153 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Jeep is fast and is used to retrieve the nuclear launch codes and return them safely to your base.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Driving over ammo crates may provide the driver with grenades to toss out the window.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Failure is not an option!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2090100/extras/bc65c51e77e1d74d0da241730d362681.poster.avif?t=1741195933\" width=320 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2090100/extras/bc65c51e77e1d74d0da241730d362681.webm?t=1741195933\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2090100/extras/bc65c51e77e1d74d0da241730d362681.mp4?t=1741195933\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
